Topic: Trading plan: ETHUSD (Ethereum)
Text:

Priority of the day: neutral position on  ETHUSD 0.48% .

2. The  ETHUSD 0.48%  rate will drop from $ 430 to $ 390. 
An alternative scenario: 
Ethereum 0.48%  may stay in flat for another day.

Topic: Father ETH weaker than son ETC
Text:
Hey guys, ETH bulls didn't managed to hold the 4H lows yesterday. We have now touched on the 61.8% fibo level, where ETH is currently trying to form its new higher higher low.  

Both on the 4H & 1H we're currently under the EMAs. So -the ETH bulls have still some work to do here. 

More important: In the  ETH/BTC              direct correlation we're now at the daily low at 0,071 -if we negate this, it means that we need to form another low until 0,055 -otherwise the weekly equilibrium will be broken with certainty. In any case, that ETH bulls need to hold the 0,071 direct correlation with  BTC 0.18% , in order to stay relatively strong.

Topic: Father ETH weaker than son ETC
Text:
Hey guys, ETH bulls didn't managed to hold the 4H lows yesterday. We have now touched on the 61.8% fibo level, where ETH is currently trying to form its new higher higher low.  

Both on the 4H & 1H we're currently under the EMAs. So -the ETH bulls have still some work to do here. 

More important: In the  ETH/BTC -5.26%  direct correlation we're now at the daily low at 0,071 -if we negate this, it means that we need to form another low until 0,055 -otherwise the weekly equilibrium will be broken with certainty. In any case, that ETH bulls need to hold the 0,071 direct correlation with  BTC 0.14% , in order to stay relatively strong.

Topic: Father ETH weaker than son ETC
Text:
Hey guys, ETH bulls didn't managed to hold the 4H lows yesterday. We have now touched on the 61.8% fibo level, where ETH is currently trying to form its new higher higher low.  

Both on the 4H & 1H we're currently under the EMAs. So -the ETH bulls have still some work to do here. 

More important: In the  ETH/BTC -5.26%  direct correlation we're now at the daily low at 0,071 -if we negate this, it means that we need to form another low until 0,055 -otherwise the weekly equilibrium will be broken with certainty. In any case, that ETH bulls need to hold the 0,071 direct correlation with  BTC -0.01% , in order to stay relatively strong.

Text:

Ethereum 1.19%  rate, along with  Bitcoin             , is in uncertainty: there is nowhere to fall and there are no buyers yet. Therefore, we are watching the crypto market, waiting for someone's initiative.
